summary:
I'm a day late but... 
Happy phannie day! I'm so proud of these two nerds. Literally everyone In the phandom knows this but if...
body:
I’m a day late but…

Happy phannie day! I’m so proud of these two nerds. Literally everyone In the phandom knows this but if you don’t know, 9 years ago Dan and Phil met for the first time. In the past 9 years they have changed millions of people’s lives and helped out so many people. Personally they have helped me find so many friends whether its in real life or on the internet. They have also inspired me to do art and I will forever be thankful. I am so glad that all of this happened. I hope you have an amazing rest of your day 💕💕💕 @danielhowell @amazingphil

summary: Hey guys im kinda upset right now. So I got a shirt from dans merch store a few months ago but I only just wore it for the first...
body: Hey guys im kinda upset right now. So I got a shirt from dans merch store a few months ago but I only just wore it for the first time a few days ago. I just washed it and the lettering started peeling immediately. I contacted customer support about it but they called it normal wear and tear. Unfortunately I wont be buying anymore of dans merch because of how expensive the cost is for such a poor quality shirt
